{"tid":1902501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突發) 一名前解放軍軍人被槍殺死亡！","createTime":"2020-02-28T11:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T18:22:11.000Z","uid":222970,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1402008e52429f8ca92f2c781e9a9385db01bb","tid":1902501,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>極大可能係國安特工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehWH7Lr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehWH7Lr.jpg&h=71a4e839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YkaZeRThFo8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYkaZeRThFo8%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=e776ec51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YkaZeRThFo8&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n據博牛社區消息：2月27日晚，一名中國公民被槍殺致死，另外五名中國男子在馬卡蒂市jazz mall附近的一家江南食府餐館受傷。當場被殺的受害者是33歲的尹X濤，他的同伴25歲的凱也受了傷。根據初步調查，受害人與犯罪嫌疑人一起進入江南食府火鍋店。其中三名嫌疑人立即逃脫，另外兩名嫌疑人在後續行動中被Barangay Bel-Air官員逮捕。菲律賓警方從被捕的兩名嫌疑人身上追回了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>三支槍支和 345,000 比索</strong></span></span>。警方仍在調查槍擊事件的動機，並大力追捕還在逃脫的三名嫌疑犯。據悉，被捕嫌犯名叫楊X雲（音譯），<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>還持有中國軍人的證件</strong></span></span>，應屬退伍軍人身份，兩伙人都屬中國人且都帶槍，其中一伙人已在馬尼拉數月，大肆搞錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nD59NNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnD59NNc.jpg&h=7826e91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NCGhcdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNCGhcdT.jpg&h=9b045029&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LPpnoky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLPpnoky.jpg&h=5c551380&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrPq5yU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrPq5yU.jpg&h=9c14eb53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Gwdu0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Gwdu0A.jpg&h=30e20ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Av5BsNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAv5BsNg.jpg&h=40b7af90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38334ea6c2867a274094c2a63d0af30f06d6c0fd","tid":1902501,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">皇</span></span>"},{"pid":"560d6f02090ccbe063260b30b90348ae1e473214","tid":1902501,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38334ea6c2867a274094c2a63d0af30f06d6c0fd","tid":1902501,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">皇</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天</span></span>"},{"pid":"a96939322fbb773745f13cb6757db80fdd5cad4d","tid":1902501,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"560d6f02090ccbe063260b30b90348ae1e473214","tid":1902501,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38334ea6c2867a274094c2a63d0af30f06d6c0fd","tid":1902501,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">皇</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天</span></span>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T11:18:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-siz